node.text:
Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico
@roth.azulik @byroth_ 
📽 Shot by: @loganstrongarms @cshep @reme_martyr 
🧘🏽‍♀️ @lizzymcole @travelwithadrien @reepetite @emchenyoga @zoejanemitchell @tomjauncey @julianmjung @racheltudoryoga 
🎶 No More - lwfi

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by BEAUTIFUL HOTELS on July 29, 2021 tagging @theyoungvillas.

node.text:
Daydreaming of this luxurious Balinese hideaway at The Young Villas. 🍃 This quiet retreat is in Canggu, just between Batu Balong and Brawa, where you have everything that you need from plush beddings, a private pool, and an inviting poolside outdoor shower. 💦 Be delighted with the well-appointed rooms and curated spaces that are great for those who are looking for IG-worthy nooks and crannies. 👀 

When was your last visit to Indonesia? Share your experience below! 🇮🇩 

📍 @theyoungvillas, Canggu, Indonesia

node.text:
Wilding out with @venelin_k at the Giraffe Manor. 😜 Awaken to the sounds of nature and wait for the herd of friendly Rothschild’s Giraffes to stop over during breakfast before they make their way to their expansive forest sanctuary. 🦒

Regarded as the ‘most Instagrammed properties in the world,’ this hidden retreat in the Langata suburb of Nairobi dates back to the 1930s with its classy façade and stately gardens. 🍃 

Have you ever been on a safari trip before? Would you stay here? 🐾 

📽️ @venelin_k
📍 Giraffe Manor, @thesafaricollection
🎶 Master KG - Jerusalema

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by BEAUTIFUL HOTELS on July 28, 2021 tagging @capellahanoi.

node.text:
Enter the enchanting halls of @capellahanoi and be intrigued by its exclusive cocoon of tranquility. 🍃 Get inspired and marvel at the 47 art nouveau suites, each individually designed by renowned architect Bill Bensley for that glamorous touch. ✨ 

Live out your opera star dreams when you stay at one of four special Opera Suites that have exciting features like a full-sized bar, alfresco terraces overlooking the Hoàn Kiếm District, and even rooftop jacuzzis! 💦

💡 BH tip: Get a feel of the ‘Roaring 20s’ when you visit the Diva’s Lounge—a 1920’s inspired cocktail bar that serves handcrafted drinks and Vietnamese tapas.

📍 @capellahanoi, Vietnam

node.text:
Soaking up this amazing view of the ocean with @amorea__ at the Hilton Seychelles Northolme. 🛁 Enjoy unlimited access to the turquoise waters of this tropical haven where you can feast on authentic Creole dishes and toast to a life well-lived. 🥂 

💡 BH tip: Book a treatment at the eforea Spa for that ultra-luxe experience by ELEMIS.

📽️ @amorea__
📍 @hiltonnortholme, Seychelles
🎶 Absofacto - Dissolve (JBroadway Remix)

node.text:
Living our lush jungle paradise dreams at these ‘CoCo Houses’ here at the ArtVillas Costa Rica. 🍃 Inhale the unadulterated air of the Earth at this luxurious retreat that is situated in the middle of the wild forests and crystal-clear beaches. 🌊 

Fitness buff? Build a relationship with your body through the different activities available onsite, or train with the world class fitness experts at the state-of-the-art fitness studio. 💪🏻 

Have you been to Central America before? Would you stay here? 🇨🇷 

📸 @boysplaynice
📍 @artvillascostarica, Osa Costa Rica

node.text:
Cozying up with @cfunk44 at the Tennessee Treehouse. 🔥 Swipe to see what our idea of Netflix and chill looks like! 📺 This secluded cabin in the woods is hidden away from the busy streets of the city and is just a few moments away from a gorgeous hiking trail to the nearby lake. 💦 

💡 BH tip: Depending on the weather, the lake is also a great place to kayak! Don’t have your own? You can always rent from one of the nearby establishments. 🛶 

📸 @cfunk44
📍 @chltreehouse, Tennessee, USA

node.text:
Getting all fired up with @dirtanglass at The Hidden Retreat. 🔥 This former fisherman’s cottage from the 1920s is a modern-day sanctuary that is close to the beach and local wineries in the area. ☀️ 

Staying in? Light up one of the two wood fireplaces in the property and lounge around in your pajamas for that perfect lazy afternoon treat. 😌

💡 BH tip: Bring your favorite movies with you and watch them with your favorite people on the 100” projector screen! 🍿 

📽️ @dirtandglass
📍 @thehiddenretreatny, New York, USA
🎶 Can't Take My Eyes Off Of You - Lauryn Hill

location.name: The Hidden Retreat at Port Jefferson, NY

node.text:
Sleeping under the stars with @reneeroaming at the Panorama Glass Lodge. 🌠 Located just a few hours away from Reykjavik, this Scandinavian cabin igloo lets you marvel at the everchanging skies of Iceland from the comforts of your soft king-sized bed. 🌌 

Aside from the expansive views of the Nordic sky, you can also see Volcano Hekla, the highland mountains, and the nearby serene river from your cozy cottage. 😌

💡 BH tip: This is a pet-friendly property!

Would you stay here when you visit Iceland? 🇮🇸 

📸 @reneeroaming
📍 @panoramaglasslodge, Iceland

node.text:
Going on a Jamaican escapade with @coreymus at the Couples Resorts. 🇯🇲 Are you also dreaming of visiting Jamaica one day? There are many beautiful spots scattered across this tropical paradise that will surely take your breath away like famed Seven Mile Beach, the mesmerizing Dunn's River Falls, and the astounding peaks of the Blue and John Crow Mountains National Park. 🌄

Check out this awesome room tour! 😮 This all-inclusive resort gives you endless possibilities in celebrating the most precious moments of your life. ❣️

Dubbed as one of the ‘Best Caribbean Hotel Spas’ by Travel + Leisure, the Oasis Spa is the ultimate indulgence with its nourishing treatments and open-air thatched huts on the beach. 🍃 So if you're looking for that perfect spa date, this is the right spot for you! 🧖‍♂️

When are you booking that next honeymoon trip? Would you stay here? 👫🏻

📽️ @coreymus
📍 @couplesresorts, Jamaica @visitjamaica
🎶 Charlie Peacock - New Day (feat. Grant Parker)

node.text:
Admiring this lovely view of the ocean with @voyagerguru at The Residence Maldives. 💦 Nestled on the pristine waters of the Gaafu Alifu Atoll, this private island gives you unmatched access to paradise on Earth with its aquamarine waters and white sand beaches! 🏖️ 

This luxury haven is also the first location of the Spa by Clarins in the Maldives where you can avail world-class treatments developed by the renowned French skincare brand. 🍃 

💡 BH tip: Book the Beach Pool Villa for direct access to the beach!

📸 @voyagerguru
📍 @theresidencemaldives

node.text:
Escape to paradise here at @potatoheadbali. 🌴 Desa Potato Head is a ‘creative village’ set on the golden shores of Bali where ethereal escapism awaits. 🍃 

This innovative space was designed by David Gianotten of @oma.eu with sustainability and cultural immersion in mind. ✨ Get inspired as you ‘Work from Paradise’ at the Potato Head Studios—an all-inclusive residential program designed for artists to unleash their unlimited creative prowess the desa (village) will provide you everything that you need at your fingertips. 🙌🏻 

Are you also a creator who needs to change up your WFH setup? Get in on this slice of nirvana and book that residency now! 😎 

📸 @allisamazing
📍 @potatoheadbali, Bali, Indonesia

node.text:
Getting the best views of Niagara Falls with @s_saamm at the Sheraton Fallsview. 🇨🇦 Can you hear the glorious sounds of this iconic waterfall? 💦 This recently renovated luxury stay has spectacular views of the falls from your balcony and direct access to the lively halls of Casino Niagara. 🎲 

💡 BH tip: Up for an adventure? Visit the nearby Fallsview Indoor Waterpark with your family! 💙

📸 @sheratonfallsview and @s_saamm 
📍 @sheratonfallsview, Ontario, Canada
